short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Very simple change tab title with domain name for KeePass Auto-Type

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Very SIMPLE Chrome Extension to :
* Display in browser tab title the domain name (and tls usage when active)
* Simplify KeePass Auto-Type recognition (remember to fill KeePass URL fields)
* Quickly see the domain name (limit phishing)

Open-Source code : https://github.com/gujou/ChromeExt4KeePass
